::Aerotaur::
     "Shhh!  I'm keeping an eye on them but... oh well now they've seen 
Windlord.  We might s well go out there and try to help that poor little 
squirrel."  He heads out from behind the trees and slowly walks over toward 
Scrat.  He kept his hands turned with the palms up in the universal symbol of 
peace.  "Can I help you at all?"
